    "created_at": "2016-08-19T21:03:55Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-08-19T21:03:55Z",
    "body": "I'm running into a similar issue where calling hide in fullscreen mode renders a black screen. I tried calling setFullScreen(false) right after the hide call, but the setFullScreen call causes the window to be shown again. Is there a way to mimic the \"close and leave full screen\" behavior, similar to other mac apps, but have it \"hide and leave full screen\" instead?\n"
  },
